title: Shed
content:
Shed may refer to:

  • The Shed key used in the Creature of Fenkenstrain quest to open the shed in the backyard of Fenkenstrain's Castle.
  • The Key used in the Witch's House quest to open her shed.
  • The gardening shed on the grounds of Sinclair Mansion.
  • The shed near Edgeville that is unlocked with the Brass key to get into the Edgeville Dungeon.
  • The shed near Grim's house during the 2015 Halloween event.
  • The shed leading to Zanaris in the Lumbridge Swamp.
  • Tool Leprechauns were originally said to teleport your stored items into the Lumbridge Swamp shed.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.

rawContent:
'''Shed''' may refer to:

*The [[Shed key]] used in the [[Creature of Fenkenstrain]] [[quest]] to open the shed in the backyard of [[Fenkenstrain's Castle]].
*The [[Key (Witch's House)|Key]] used in the [[Witch's House]] quest to open her shed.
*The gardening shed on the grounds of [[Sinclair Mansion]].
*The shed near [[Edgeville]] that is unlocked with the [[Brass key]] to get into the [[Edgeville Dungeon]].
*The shed near [[Grim]]'s house during the [[2015 Halloween event]].
*The shed leading to [[Zanaris]] in the [[Lumbridge Swamp]].
*[[Tool Leprechaun]]s were originally said to teleport your stored items into the Lumbridge Swamp shed.
